{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/EPost.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.replaceEPostHeadBot?\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">replaceEPostHeadBot?</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">target </span><span class=\"fn\">head</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">args</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">Meta.Sym.SymM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"When the exception postcondition is `⊥`, the RHS of a `pre ⊑ EPost.Cons.head ⊥ x₁ … xₙ` goal is\npropositionally—but not definitionally—equal to `⊥`. This rewrites the goal to `pre ⊑ ⊥`,\nconstructing the equality proof from `EPost.Cons.head_bot` (for the head projection) and\n`bot_apply` (for each excess argument).\n\nThe proof term is built directly with `mkApp`/`mkConst` and instances extracted from the existing\ngoal, avoiding `mkAppM`/instance synthesis (which is both expensive and unable to unify `max`-of-\nuniverse-variable instance levels in the abstract-monad setting).\n\n`head`/`args` come from `rhs.withApp`, where `rhs = EPost.Cons.head eh et ⊥ x₁ … xₙ`, and `target`\nis the full `pre ⊑ rhs` entailment. Returns the rewritten goal, or `none` if `args[2]` is not `⊥`\nor the lattice instances are not in the expected shape (the caller then falls through). ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/EPost.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.replaceEPostHeadBot?","kind":"def","line":44,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.replaceEPostHeadBot?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/EPost.lean#L44-L106"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">partial def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/EPost.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.peelEPostTailChain\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">peelEPostTailChain</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">curr</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">idx</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a> := <span class=\"fn\">0</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Prod\">×</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Peel a chain of `.tail` projections, returning the base `EPost` and the number of tails. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/EPost.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.peelEPostTailChain","kind":"opaque","line":36,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.peelEPostTailChain","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/EPost.lean#L36-L42"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/EPost.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.mkEPostAtIndex\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">mkEPostAtIndex</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">target</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">index</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Sym/SymM.html#Lean.Meta.Sym.SymM\">Meta.Sym.SymM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Get the `index`-th component from an `EPost` target. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/EPost.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.mkEPostAtIndex","kind":"def","line":27,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.mkEPostAtIndex","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/EPost.lean#L27-L34"}}],"imports":["Lean.Meta.Sym","Lean.Meta.Tactic.Replace","Std.Internal.Do"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.EPost"}